m Bolt]]\n*[[Bolt of Draining]]\n*[[Quicksilver Bolt]]\n*[[Corrosive Bolt]]\n*[[Lightning Bolt]]\n\n==History==\n*Random bolt was removed in [[0.27]]. The only enemy that had the spell was [[Mnoleg]].\n*Prior to [[0.19]], there was another monster with this spell, [[Chaos champion]].\n*Prior to [[0.18]], the player had an access to this spell through the [[rod of destruction]]. Also, [[Mnoleg]] didn't have this spell.\n*Prior to [[0.17]], [[Crystal Bolt]] was one of the possible bolts.\n*In [[0.16]], [[Corrosive Bolt]] was added to the list of possible bolts.\n*Prior to [[0.14]], Random Bolt was a level 5 spell.\n\n[[Category:Monster spells]]\n[[Category:Obsolete spells]]"}